Package concordanceExperiments

package concordanceExperiments
Experiments include:

• rejection sampling of ranking systems until a 3-concordant one is found;

• random walk in a set of 3-concordant random systems

• exhaustive generation of all 3-concordant ranking systems on four objects

Author:
R. W. R. Darling
